metadata.Plot: Mercenaries with nothing to lose are hired to rescue a bioengineer imprisoned in a cold war bunker. Upon entering the ominous facility, they find themselves in a fight for their lives when they come under attack from an unknown and deadly creature.
metadata.Actors: Jeremy Ninaber, Ethan Mitchell, Kristen Kaster
